OL,3,CGovernment introducse law to clear
OL,4,Cvictims of Post Office scandal
OL,6,FA law aimed at quashing the wrongful
OL,7,Fconvictions of sub-postmasters caught
OL,8,Fup in the IT scandal is being
OL,9,Fintroduced by the government on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FThe proposed Post Office (Horizon
OL,13,FSystem) Offences Bill "marks an
OL,14,Fimportant step forward in finally
OL,15,Fclearing" the names of hundreds of
OL,16,Fwronged branch managers who have had
OL,17,Ftheir lives "callously torn apart",
OL,18,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak said.
