OL,6,FThe legislation will exonerate those
OL,7,Fconvicted in England and Wales on the
OL,8,Fbasis of the faulty Horizon accounting
OL,9,Fsoftware in what has been branded the
OL,10,Fbiggest miscarriage of justice in
OL,11,FBritish legal history.
