OL,3,CGovernment introducse law to clear
OL,4,Cvictims of Post Office scandal
OL,6,FMore than 700 sub-postmasters were
OL,7,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,8,Fhanded criminal convictions between
OL,9,F1999 and 2015 as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,10,FHorizon IT system made it appear as
OL,11,Fthough money was missing at their
OL,12,Fbranches.
OL,14,FThe long-running saga was put in a
OL,15,Ffresh spotlight by ITV's acclaimed
OL,16,Fdrama
