OL,4,Cvictims of Post Office scandal
OL,6,FThe government hopes the Bill will
OL,7,Freceive royal assent and become law
OL,8,Fahead of MPs' summer holiday.
OL,10,FPost Office minister Kevin Hollinrake
OL,11,Fsaid: "Sub-postmasters have been
OL,12,Ffighting for justice for years, and I
OL,13,Fhope the introduction of today's
OL,14,Flegislation is the light at the end of
OL,15,Fthe tunnel they have been waiting for."
OL,17,FBusiness Secretary Kemi Badenoch said
OL,18,Fministers "won't rest until every
OL,19,Fvictim receives the compensation they
OL,20,Fare entitled to".
