OL,6,F"It is absolutely right that we sweep
OL,7,Faway the convictions wrongly given to
OL,8,Fpostmasters on the basis of bad
OL,9,Fevidence, and it is a disgrace that
OL,10,Fthey were ever pursued by the Post
OL,11,FOffice," she said.
OL,13,FMinisters have decided the scale of
OL,14,Fthe scandal is so great that the usual
OL,15,Fprocess of individuals going through
OL,16,Fthe courts would take too long.
